Malaysian Virgin Grade 6A
description: Malaysian Hair is a highly sought after texture and a very popular option among celebrities. Malaysian hair has an extremely luxurious feel and is sleek and shiny, but not excessively shiny. Its luster is low to medium-similar to Brazilian hair. Malaysian hair holds curls extremely well without the use of products. It is generally dark brown although some bundles may having lighter ends. This hair blends very well with most hair types including African American. No frizzing due to humidity. It is available in straight, body wave and curly textures.

name: Peruvian Grade 6A Virgin
description: Peruvian Hair is the ultimate multi-purpose hair! It's extremely soft and ultimately feather light! You can have up to five bundles of a Peruvian hair installed yet still have a manageable style. This hair is more course in texture than Indian or Brazilian hair and its luster is low to medium. It blends very well with African-American relaxed hair textures and medium Caucasian hair textures. Peruvian hair is very luxurious and another one of our favorites..

name: Brazilian Lace Closure Straight
description: U Part Closures are excellent for filling the crown part of weaves and u part wigs! If you’re a frequent weave wearer, you know blending your hair makes all the difference when making your install flawless. Texture isn’t an issue when wearing lace closures. Versatile parting is also an advantage, closures allow you to wear bangs, middle parts, and side parts in one hair weave. Color is a go because you no longer have to worry about damaging your hair, you can choose to experiment with any color that you desire! Low Maintenance, Perfect for protective styling!!
